706322f-a.title: Brooklyn: President Street - Prospect Park West
706322f-a.text:
President Street, south side, (right) west of Prospect Park West, to and including Eighth Ave., showing in the right background the steeples of St. Francis Xavier R.C. Church. This general view west was taken from the Knights of Columbus Building, located at the N.W. corner of Prospect Park West (No. 1) and President Street.
June 1926.
Brown Brothers.
